---
title: Juicy Steak with Roasted Veggies and Sour Cream and Chive Mash
description: This steak will be perfectly juicy and tender after pan-searing each side and then a few minutes in the oven. Roasting the vegetables with the steak make this dish extra easy and fabulous. Look out for this sour cream and chive mash too - it’s an absolute winner.
